Thank you to everyone who supported me throughout the creation process of this. This is only the fourth map I've ever made, but I am definitely proud of it despite it having a few issues. If there are any major issues please contact me on discord at PrisonNightmare#7061.

- EDIT -

There were some things that were fucked up that I wanted to change. A list of what I changed is below:

- Changed HDR settings so they aren't blindingly bright
- Fixed abused skips in the map (fuck you wilkins xd)
- Fixed B4 trigger_multiple zones
- Added easter egg for friend since apparently he tested the map and I completely forgot about it
